  <brief_title>Sevoflurane-Remifentanil Anaesthesia. The Risk of Post Operative Nausea</brief_title>
  <official_title>Postoperative Nausea and Vomiting Are Similar When Propofol or Sevoflurane Are Used as Adjuvant to Remifentanil During Anaesthesia for Gynaecological Surgery</official_title>
